items.title: WATCH:  F-35 jet crashes in Alaska, pilot ejects safely
items.description: Video circulating online shows the fighter jet crashing into flames at Eielson Air Force Base and the pilot parachuting to the ground.

items.title: F-35 crashes at Eielson Air Force Base in Alaska as pilot ejects safely
items.description: An Air Force F-35 fighter jet crashed at Eielson Air Force Base in Alaska on Tuesday as the pilot ejected safely, officials said.

items.title: WATCH:  Over 100 kids attend boozy house party at school principal's home: Cops
items.description: The homeowner was quickly identified to be Elizabeth Hill-Brodigan, the principal of nearby Roosevelt Elementary School, police said.

items.title: Tree trimmer dead after getting caught in wood chipper at Florida town hall
items.description: A tree trimmer died after getting caught in a wood chipper while trimming trees at a town hall near Miami, officials said.
